headline: Subtle Target Hike Shows JP Morgan Cautious Optimism On NXP Semiconductors N.V. (NXPI)
summary: NXP Semiconductors N.V. (NASDAQ:NXPI) is among the most profitable semiconductor stocks to buy. On October 29, 2025, Harlan Sur, an analyst at JP Morgan, increased the price target on NXP Semiconductors N.V. (NASDAQ:NXPI) to $245 from $240, while reaffirming a ‘Neutral’ rating on the stock.
